# Storage Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get all storage items (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/storage
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get storage item by ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/storage/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create storage item (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/storage
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "key": "exampleKey",
  "value": "exampleValue"
}

### Update storage item (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/storage/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "value": "newValue"
}

### Delete storage item (protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/storage/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
